uting to the country's AI infrastructure.\n*   **Sector-Focused Specialists:** Firms such as Fractal Analytics (decision intelligence), Locus (logistics), and Staqu Technologies (public safety) are providing deep domain expertise.\n\nAs enterprise adoption of AI accelerates, the ability to deliver full-scale, reliable AI solutions is what will distinguish leading companies in 2026. The focus has shifted from experimentation to execution-focused AI adoption, promising a transformative impact on various industries."}],"role":"model"},"finish_reason":"STOP","grounding_metadata":{"grounding_chunks":[{"web":{"title":"augustinfotech.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG7_WaGsVVGr9Cgf-yvJE_9yoC4nqzO6cNdxVYMcQ6OyaZnbPUPeTM-wIR4QDwYYkuqFsD-QDHMVuyL887JAgHhoqeVwI4XLmuBsn400I-Uk6AxCNRuaNgo_IxkwCKi7VAbIUWrksjQgNnZc_dIRoFJldAKmp3d_oxn4kj2nw61r16yRsg4KsU="}},{"web":{"title":"innovationm.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFH9BOEF2hJHPerZ3Nsc9y4y2T6mJ_4CWc6oXmjBCBQjDMyDH8npddi0F20AI0GLFCnmyvznfGANkQoy1XFIplyjtDFUxVOIyWki7nfuDTbl6eC64_Hhx5MlLp30A1qlSOg-l9zfV6lJRtDoCVj28a9D4RsULUpsNCgxdduWOLgZ0g="}},{"web":{"title":"codeneptune.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEcHOEgh57Tt75pZGURqr-VtZvI4Gj2sfn1YpE49-oNK7GEcoSvKtrhXZhDHERUg6uH9qH9NPFiAItCgSCFC0YTKz9EY-gZokYjbxocvv5DRcVCBS-SwIYSUcA6oTu9wDznPDPf7U5nKzNpisx5kLLH4R_kwhQ_u4W0PH6jBHJ28g=="}},{"web":{"title":"medium.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFFpFXcMXCjqydj6XbZrH7U4W-UBqfi-6Va0GkrjUT3WpptvpGyRuVlUwcUn8EDEbH-FYCY3e-IFnSQ6O8K-w18Tqvfp8j4NfVXy9fVRDi1fpjaLCWpY6kwG5PdFGS64umVMFx2No5uAOJ_zNNi6LWw9aWLx0sPdeQLD3gnsyDYqKdPws1L49HhyoMch46d5Aj13rs9Kkt_HvL3ARG2d34feMYBAKlW5Vo15dGq"}},{"web":{"title":"ksolves.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGy_THTTmPmmzhlCfRCrU3GEPrGps_FrxAZ9LNqlp2q5m96hTRntXP4JOy_LJZERreW34BIYXaC1JV