moving from experimentation to full-scale operationalization due to the aforementioned structural constraints. For CIOs in 2026, the focus is less on acquiring new AI tools and more on fixing the foundational issues of data, governance, and integration to use them effectively."}],"role":"model"},"finish_reason":"STOP","grounding_metadata":{"grounding_chunks":[{"web":{"title":"techrepublic.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEElh__fCSqUSmBy2vOInNlIjhjmSWzRmdNTMix73dXqdgevvCO86C4KaD8-Z2hAwXNFOsh0_atInw3bMKCvaNyqkdRJGc1tyEVELiGakRruntYvpuof99dd1zwF_6tJGFoEd_y6CJp-QgUhshATWGOpngUv-suqAKWzSHznaTMyxiqjQD_9sLDRJaF6D0J5tIr2A=="}},{"web":{"title":"indiatimes.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEFSNn8LMGCfUNbMx8rgn8EfvrNhbAgagT8GU7_Ju1CNp1ElhjJluhadiEKo9XijS9D75v2iVDAoVpOaJY9c5eoxEW1dyQCrxIACZ9eOJkRqFqigc0veccL4Qq9nzB-9l8otbHL2Xvv9fRt5K8U0fx56H7eXkuxxyFtwTUtiuUsKTUV3Kyr1xK3MfkhqUAdzMItOnj25p6pkHA-q3Zl_0jqAS4MG7Zf2fJWKooCoOnBuek02x_R-Eb94bHXxPouZgF90NotZUyD-zZbQLfu6Q=="}},{"web":{"title":"economictimes.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHhpdrzY6pvbuzkPZFIuFCUhYFfAD4eCVpezOKvP_cEpml8unIDIkeoVPOXyeLiVZTLkvts_DggYLFzfBuKJprXNQgNw8IfaREFNOBB43Kiuz2LueaqeboyIzKbwxCAVx0xCXAYEFbU5ISTdFQTDhLJiDJPjeaFu1GBEDh8i02GSqy6qtOlLC2QiDwa7NvfcDfrmAO7Uwp5GZilzIlxg00BtGbEQFMw62BuiMCVx2KjVRE50cwGjR-4dy5yCRK5xoHpLTiJRiKlK3TmEySMrFSrVoM="}},{"web":{"title":"etedge-insights.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF86JOSM6O_xYjR1mU6r5pzoTUaVxevoC7pYx4TmmeBBDW4I-Y-lDEQt0I-6OrB_zOl5kAnompejKjxqHMJCYF0WuPO9tyk5JTzCGR-aNqj2gSukZczXAZGOpbH8ddNHHictHpsFH45h_rDVOSB0i4xUy3Md4jFh3SA_PBntewe97Z5GXpJEhW8XQlhEJQgIUha-PDg20gbhWW3Fm1BleRWW1fb6ZywTN5X2VwygYMTGb5X216sYa-I37x_RIA1HvUPvY_buCGprSzvIBEB"}},{"web":{"title":"hdfcfund.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHiFWutyG9iTDC5BC7slmWk0vzZ5HrHv7nAtzt